lude%20reducing%20your%20food%20waste%20with%20pre-portioned%20foods%20and%20helping%20you%20discover%20new%20recipes%20and%20cooking%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20are%20the%20cons%20of%20meal%20kit%20delivery%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20biggest%20con%20of%20meal%20kit%20delivery%20is%20the%20price.%20With%20rising%20grocery%20costs%2C%20you%20may%20not%20save%20much%20money%20buying%20ingredients%20yourself%2C%20especially%20when%20you%20factor%20in%20food%20waste.%20Speaking%20of%20waste%2C%20the%20kits'%20packaging%20is%20substantial%20and%20not%20always%20made%20of%20eco-friendly%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeal%20kits%20also%20require%20preparation%20time%2C%20though%20many%20services%20also%20offer%20freshly%20prepared%20meals.%20Lastly%2C%20the%20services%20have%20limited%20customization%20options%2C%20which%20may%20be%20hard%20for%20picky%20eaters%20or%20individuals%20with%20unique%20dietary%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20are%20the%20different%20types%20of%20meal%20kit%20delivery%20services%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20standard%20meal%20kit%20contains%20ingredients%20and%20a%20recipe%20with%20varying%20levels%20of%20preparation%20required.%20It%20ranges%20from%20pre-cut%20ingredients%20that%20you%20just%20toss%20in%20a%20bowl%20and%20season%2C%20to%20essentially%20a%20curated%20grocery%20order%20that%20you%20chop%20and%20prep.%20While%20kits%20are%20still%20popular%2C%20a%20new%20common%20option%20is%20freshly%20prepared%20meals%20that%20you%20just%20pop%20in%20the%20microwave%20or%20oven.%20Some%20brands%20even%20offer%20frozen%20meals.%20There%20are%20also%20hybrid%20meals%20that%20require%20minimal%20preparation%20and%20are%20mostly%20ready-to-heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Blue%20Apron%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20meal%20of%20lettuce%20wraps%20from%20Blue%20Apron%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64da59641f51cc00196911d9%3Ffo