Has%20Turnover%20of%20Rs%2010%20Cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUntil%20three%20years%20back%2C%20Sukhwinder%20Singh%20had%20not%20heard%20about%20biofortified%20seeds%20%E2%80%93%20seeds%20that%20have%20been%20bred%20to%20have%20higher%20levels%20of%20certain%20nutrients%20like%20iron%20and%20zinc.%20The%20farmer%20has%20been%20successfully%20growing%20wheat%20on%20his%205.5-acre%20landholding%20using%20these%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20decision%20to%20switch%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%20was%20prompted%20by%20his%20concerns%20over%20the%20rampant%20use%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20which%20not%20only%20harm%20the%20environment%20but%20also%20pose%20health%20risks%20to%20consumers.%20He%20chose%20to%20invest%20in%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20which%20are%20rich%20in%20zinc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20remarkable%20outcomes%20of%20Sukhwinder%E2%80%99s%20adoption%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%20is%20the%20improvement%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20produce.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20children%20find%20the%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(chapati)%20made%20from%20the%20wheat%20grown%20with%20biofortified%20seeds%20tastier.%20This%20has%20not%20only%20enhanced%20the%20taste%20of%20my%20produce%20but%20also%20ensured%20that%20my%20children%20consume%20safe%20and%20nutritious%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2049-year-old%20resident%20of%20Bambhera%20village%2C%20Sitapur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prateek%20and%20Aishwarya%20studying%20plants%20with%20farmers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364805%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrateek%20and%20Aishwarya%20decided%20to%20fortify%20seeds%20with%20essential%20nutrients%20like%20zinc%2C%20iron%2C%20manganese%2C%20boron%2C%20and%20copper.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%20has%20also%20reduced%20his%20input%20costs%20by%20reducing%20his%20dependency%20on%20urea%20fertiliser.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20had%20to%20add%20three%20rags%20of%20urea%20on%20one%20acre%20of%20land%2C%20now%20I%20only%20have%20to%20add%20as%20little%20as%20half%20a%20rag%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESukhwinder%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20yield%20per%20acre%20may%20be%20slightly%20lower%20compared%20to%20conventional%20seeds%2C%20the%20overall%20benefits%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326709%2Fcultyvate-agri-tech-solution-helps-paddy-farmers-reduce-water-waste-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduced%20input%20costs%20and%20improved%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20far%20outweigh%20any%20minor%20differences%20in%20productivity.%20Besides%2C%20I%20am%20earning%20Rs%202%2C600%20per%20quintal%20instead%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20rates%20for%20regular%20wheat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Sukhwinder%2C%20at%20least%2015%2C000%20small-landholding%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20thanks%20to%20Aishwarya%20and%20Prateek%20Rastogi%2C%20who%20are%20promoting%20innovative%20and%20eco-friendly%20farming%20methods%20that%20benefit%20both%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20food%20we%20eat%20daily%20nutritious%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20after%20completing%20higher%20studies%20and%20gaining%20entrepreneurship%20training%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Prateek%20felt%20a%20strong%20calling%20towards%20uplifting%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20in%20his%20home%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20advised%20to%20venture%20into%20more%20developed%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%20and%20Gujarat%20for%20ease%20of%20business%2C%20he%20strived%20to%20focus%20on%20central%20and%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20regions%20that%20still%20required%20substantial%20advancement%20in%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20for%20the%20corporate%20world%20for%20a%20year%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20moved%20to%20his%20ancestral%20village%20in%20Sitapur%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Aishwarya%2C%20who%20is%20an%20alumna%20of%20IHM%20Bombay%20where%20she%20studied%20food%20sciences%20and%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20out%20to%20live%20out%20of%20an%20agri-warehouse.%20This%20is%20where%20they%20learnt%20more%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342901%2Ffarmer-income-success-lcb-fertilizers-biofertiliser-navyakosh-akshay-shrivastav-iit-kanpur-labs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenges%20faced%20by%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRural%20visits%20are%20close%20to%20our%20hearts.%20We%20love%20spending%20time%20in%20villages%2C%20cooking%20by%20a%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20chulha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(firewood%20stove)%2C%20and%20sharing%20stories%20with%20farmers.%20I%20also%20grew%20up%20eating%20farm%20produce%20that%20was%20sent%20to%20us%20from%20our%20village%20to%20our%20home%20in%20Lucknow.%20These%20experiences%20fuel%20our%20passion%20for%20our%20startup%20and%20our%20commitment%20to%20improving%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20farming%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20he%20observed%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20farmers%20toil%20day%20and%20night%20to%20grow%20food%2C%20it%20lacks%20sufficient%20nutritional%20content.%20India%20faces%20severe%20micronutrient%20deficiencies%20due%20to%20essential%20nutrients%20lacking%20in%20crop%20outputs%2C%20leading%20to%20health%20issues%20like%20anaemia%20and%20stunted%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20At%20least%2015%2C000%20small-landholding%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20biofortified%20seeds.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364806%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20At%20least%2015%2C000%20small-landholding%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20biofortified%20seeds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%205%20(2019-21)%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1795421%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E57%20percent%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20women%20aged%2015-49%20in%20India%20are%20anaemic%20whereas%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1806601%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E35.5%20percent%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20children%20under%20five%20years%20of%20age%20are%20stunted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAishwarya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20untapped%20power%20in%20the%20food%20we%20consume%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20our%20diet%20is%20%3Cem%3Eroti%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20rice.%20Looking%20at%20the%20anaemia%20and%20stunting%20data%20of%20our%20country%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20we%20do%20not%20get%20enough%20nutrients%20from%20the%20food%20we%20eat.%20I%20strongly%20believe%20that%20nutrition%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20luxury%20but%20a%20right%20for%20us%20all%20Indians.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20everyone%20deserves%20access%20to%2C%20and%20cannot%20be%20a%20privilege%20for%20a%20few.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealising%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20improve%20crop%20nutrition%20naturally%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20fortify%20seeds%20of%20crops%20such%20as%20maize%2C%20paddy%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296561%2Fmahalingam-govindaraj-scientist-develops-first-biofortified-pearl-millet-bajra-wins-award%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinger%20millets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20essential%20nutrients%20like%20zinc%2C%20iron%2C%20manganese%2C%20boron%2C%20and%20copper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20understanding%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20Greenday%20in%20January%202020%2C%20aiming%20to%20bring%20systemic%20innovation%20and%20enhance%20crop%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EImproving%20nutritional%20value%20through%20biofortification%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vision%20of%20Greenday%2C%20Prateek%20says%2C%20was%20simple%20yet%20impactful.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20improve%20the%20nutritional%20quality%20of%20crops%20while%20empowering%20farmers%20economically.%20By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20were%20not%20only%20able%20to%20enhance%20their%20income%20through%20premium%20pricing%20but%20also%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20addressing%20widespread%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342444%2Fias-officer-avi-prasad-community-programme-to-fight-malnutrition-katni-madhya-pradesh-donate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissues%20of%20malnutrition%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20developed%20through%20crossbreeding%20for%20nutritional%20benefits%20and%20climate%20resilience%2C%20showed%20promising%20results%20in%20increasing%20essential%20nutrient%20levels%20by%20up%20to%2080%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20introducing%20zinc%20soil%20bacteria%20to%20enrich%20the%20soil%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20seeds%20enabled%20plants%20to%20absorb%20more%20nutrients%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20significantly%20higher%20nutritional%20content%20in%20the%20harvested%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364813%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%2C%20Prateek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20we%20found%20that%20the%20baseline%20levels%20of%20zinc%20in%20the%20traditional%20variety%20of%20wheat%20is%20around%2028%20parts%20per%20million%20whereas%2C%20it%20is%2045%20parts%20per%20million%20in%20the%20newer%20bio%20fortified%20seeds.%20We%20also%20add%20a%20zinc%20soil%20bacteria%20to%20the%20soil%20which%20helps%20mobilise%20the%20naturally%20available%20zinc%20and%20bring%20it%20to%20the%20roots.%20This%20increases%20zinc%20base%20levels%20to%2050-55%20parts%20per%20million%20%E2%80%93%20an%20increment%20of%20about%2080%20percent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20every%20seed%20will%20have%20its%20own%20benefits%20and%20drawbacks.%20These%20seeds%20give%20almost%2080%20percent%20more%20nutritional%20value%20but%20farmers%20may%20have%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20of%204%20to%205%20percent%20in%20yield.%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349986%2Fprabhat-kumar-sumarth-ngo-bihar-horticulture-training-for-farmers-double-income-cash-crops%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epremium%20rates%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20such%20produce%20covers%20up%20the%20yield%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20collaborations%20with%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20across%20regions%20like%20Gorakhpur%2C%20Basti%2C%20Gonda%2C%20Barabanki%2C%20and%20others%2C%20the%20initiative%20not%20only%20promoted%20the%20adoption%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%20but%20also%20provided%20holistic%20services%20ranging%20from%20soil%20analysis%20to%20crop%20selection%20in%20order%20to%20boost%20crop%20nutrient%20content%20naturally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20impact%20created%20by%20their%20startup%2C%20Aishwarya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20spending%202.5%20years%20in%20Sitapur%20closely%20working%20with%20farmers%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20potential%20in%20something%20as%20small%20as%20a%20seed.%20We%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20massive%20impact%20by%20working%20for%20our%20farmers.%20Seeing%20their%20dedication%20first%20hand%20has%20been%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experience.%20Their%20hard%20work%20fuels%20our%20passion%20to%20turn%20our%20brand%20into%20a%20movement%20that%20not%20only%20improves%20health%20but%20also%20supports%20livelihoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Greenday.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726494464000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D364767%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lucknow-based%20Aishwarya%20Bhatnagar%20and%20Prateek%20Rastogi%20run%20Greenday%20to%20promote%20innovative%20farming%20methods%20and%20biofortified%20seeds%20that%20benefit%20both%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Foreign%20Insurgent%20Arrested%2C%20Says%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%3B%20Lie%2C%20He's%20A%20Refugee%2C%20Says%20Kuki%20Group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20today%20congratulated%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20for%20what%20he%20said%20was%20the%20arrest%20of%20a%20%26quot%3BBurmese%20national%26quot%3B%20who%20is%20allegedly%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Myanmar-based%20insurgent%20group%20Kuki%20National%20Army%20(Burma)%2C%20or%20KNA(B).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20Students'%20Organisation%20(KSO-GHQ)%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20man%20being%20referred%20to%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20KNA(B)%20is%20a%20registered%20refugee%2C%20who%20fled%20from%20the%20conflict%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20appreciate%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20who%20arrested%20one%20Burmese%20national%2C%20KNA(B).%20As%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20I%20have%20been%20continuously%20saying%20since%20the%20beginning%20that%20the%20present%20crisis%20in%20Manipur%20has%20a%20foreign%20hand.%20Some%20people%20believe%20it%2C%20some%20don't.%20I%20appreciate%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20for%20apprehending%20the%20foreign%20national%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20valley-dominant%20Meitei%20community%2C%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comment%20drew%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20KSO%2C%20whose%20spokesperson%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20young%20man%20who%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20called%20a%20KNA(B)%20member%20was%20indeed%20from%20Myanmar%2C%20but%20registered%20in%20the%20official%20records%20along%20with%20his%20thumb%20prints%20and%20other%20details%20as%20a%20refugee.%20The%20KSO%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20knows%20the%20man%20is%20a%20registered%20refugee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20not%20given%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvkl1bcig_churachandpur_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20Myanmar%20nationals%20have%20crossed%20into%20Manipur%20and%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%2C%20fleeing%20the%20conflict%20between%20pro-democracy%20ethnic%20rebels%20and%20the%20junta.%20The%20Assam%20Rifles%20guards%20the%20Indo-Myanmar%20border%20as%20well%20as%20conduct%20counter-insurgency%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20KSO%20general%20headquarters%20is%20shocked%20and%20surprised%20at%20the%20same%20time%20because%20someone%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20without%20inquiring%20more%20details%20about%20what's%20happening%2C%20made%20such%20a%20silly%20judgment.%20The%20apprehended%20person...%20who%20is%20from%20Myanmar%20-%20of%20course%20he%20is%20a%20foreigner%20-%20but%20has%20been%20here%20registered%20as%20a%20refugee%2C%20which%20was%20accepted%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20KSO%20spokesperson%20told%20NDTV%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20all%20the%20details.%20In%20spite%20of%20all%20the%20details%20available%20on%20social%20media%20as%20well...%20when%20we%20have%20all%20these%20details%2C%20why%20would%20a%20refugee%20be%20caught%3F%20And%20then%20after%20that%20brand%20him%20a%20militant%20or%20outlaw%3F%20This%20is%20so%20wrong.%20I%20think%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20should%20be%20more%20focussed%20and%20inquire%20into%20the%20tape%20leak%20than%20any%20other%20problem%20just%20to%20deviate%20from%20what%20is%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20leaked%20audio%20tapes%20that%20purportedly%20has%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20starting%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audio%20tapes%20have%20been%20submitted%20to%20an%20inquiry%20panel%20under%20the%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20and%20those%20who%20provided%20the%20tapes%20have%20given%20affidavits%20saying%20the%20content%20is%20genuine%2C%20according%20to%20reports%20by%20the%20news%20website%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20has%20called%20the%20audio%20tapes%20%26quot%3Bdoctored%26quot%3B%2C%20meant%20to%20sabotage%20peace%20plans%20in%20the%20ethnic%20violence-hit%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20top%20sources%20had%20told%20NDTV%20no%20KNA(B)%20member%20was%20arrested%20in%20Manipur's%20Chandel%2C%20as%20claimed%20by%20some%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20villages%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20the%20hills%20surrounding%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20valley.%20The%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20community%20and%20the%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20known%20as%20Kukis%20-%20a%20term%20given%20by%20the%20British%20in%20colonial%20times%20-%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20has%20killed%20over%20220%20people%20and%20internally%20displaced%20nearly%2050%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20category%20Meiteis%20want%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category%2C%20while%20the%20Kukis%20who%20share%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20people%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20Mizoram%20want%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%2C%20citing%20discrimination%20and%20unequal%20share%20of%20resources%20and%20power%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726494240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fi70bjv88_biren-kso_625x300_16_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkna-b-insurgent-arrested-says-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-lie-hes-a-refugee-says-kuki-students-organisation-kso-6578912%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Man