t%20take%20parenting%20as%20a%20pressure.%20Slow%20down.%20It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20not%20be%20busy%20all%20the%20time.%20Let%20your%20children%20enjoy%20their%20childhood.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20world%20beyond%20gadgets%20and%20video%20games.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTravelling%20teaches%20both%20you%20and%20your%20children%20mindfulness%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20present.%20It%20helps%20you%20shed%20your%20ego%20as%20you%20come%20to%20realise%20that%20you%20are%20not%20greater%20than%20nature.%20No%20school%20can%20provide%20the%20lessons%20that%20nature%20offers.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20fosters%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20community%20bound%20by%20a%20shared%20love%20for%20the%20natural%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Nehal%20Shah%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726491246000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nehal%20Shah%2C%20an%20avid%20traveller%2C%20began%20taking%20her%20son%20on%20her%20adventures%20and%20saw%20the%20value%20of%20outdoor%20experiences%20for%20families.%20Recognising%20the%20importance%20of%20nature-based%20experiences%20for%20children%2C%20she%20founded%20Heart%20%26amp%3B%20Soil%20in%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HSBC%20India%20starts%20global%20education%20payments%3B%20direct%20payments%20to%20600%20univ%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726491051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-07%2F31%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1722411718-3248.JPG%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2F