20junior%20doctors%20pointed%20to%20the%20fresh%20charge%20of%20evidence%20tampering%20against%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20former%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20where%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%20The%20officer-in-charge%20of%20Tala%20police%20station%2C%20Abhijit%20Mondal%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20this%20connection%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20two%20new%20developments%20increase%20the%20significance%20of%20transparency%20of%20the%20meeting%20even%20more%20than%20before.%20We%20would%20like%20to%20emphasise%20on%201)%20Videography%20of%20the%20meeting%20by%20a%20separate%20videographer%20by%20both%20the%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctors%20said%2C%20reiterating%20their%20demand%20for%20videography%20of%20the%20meeting.%20Earlier%2C%20meetings%20between%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20the%20junior%20doctors%20have%20fallen%20through%20over%20their%20demand%20for%20live-streaming%20and%20videography.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20said%20this%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20because%20the%20matter%20is%20sub-judice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20fresh%20email%2C%20the%20doctors%20have%20given%20alternatives%20to%20the%20state%20government.%20They%20have%20said%20that%20if%20videography%20by%20separate%20videographers%20from%20both%20sides%20is%20not%20possible%2C%20the%20state%20government%20must%20agree%20to%20give%20the%20junior%20doctors%20the%20video%20of%20the%20proceedings%20right%20after%20the%20meeting.%20The%20state%20government%20had%20earlier%20said%20they%20would%20provide%20the%20video%20only%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20another%20option%20in%20their%20new%20email%2C%20the%20doctors%20said%20minutes%20of%20the%20meeting%20with%20full%20transcripts%20be%20recorded%20by%20both%20parties%20and%20handed%20over%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20meeting%20after%20all%20present%20sign%20them.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20state%20government%20had%20agreed%20to%20provide%20a%20signed%20copy%20of%20the%20minutes%20of%20the%20meeting.%20The%20doctors%20have%20clarified%20that%20they%20would%20bring%20their%20representatives%20to%20take%20down%20the%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20consider%20the%20above%20points%20for%20the%20meeting%20for%20our%20five%20point%20demands.%20If%20you%20are%20in%20agreement%20from%20your%20side%20kindly%20respond%20to%20this%20mail%20at%20the%20earliest.%20We%20are%20eagerly%20waiting%20for%20a%20positive%20response%20from%20your%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctors'%20body%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Chief%20Secretary%20Pant%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20the%20doctors%20that%20this%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bfifth%20and%20final%20time%26quot%3B%20the%20state%20government%20is%20reaching%20out%20to%20them%20for%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BWe%20trust%20that%20good%20sense%20will%20prevail%2C%20and%20as%20mutually%20agreed%20and%20as%20per%20your%20statement%20to%20the%20media%20day%20before-%20there%20will%20be%20no%20live%20streaming%20or%20videography%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20given%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20sub%20judice%20in%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20country.%20Instead%2C%20the%20minutes%20of%20the%20meeting%20will%20be%20recorded%20and%20signed%20by%20both%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20junior%20doctors%20protesting%20over%20the%20August%209%20incident%20have%20several%20demands%2C%20including%20the%20removal%20of%20some%20top%20state%20officials.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20earlier%20asked%20them%20to%20join%20work%20by%20September%2010%2C%20but%20they%20have%20stressed%20that%20they%20will%20not%20join%20duty%20till%20their%20demands%20are%20fulfilled.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20meetings%20planned%20between%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20junior%20doctors%20led%20to%20dramatic%20scenes.%20On%20September%2012%2C%20the%20doctors%20went%20to%20the%20state%20secretariat%20Nabanna%20to%20meet%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20but%20refused%20to%20join%20the%20meeting%20after%20they%20were%20told%20the%20proceedings%20could%20not%20be%20live-streamed.%20Visuals%20of%20Ms%20Banerjee%20waiting%20for%20the%20junior%20doctors%20went%20viral%20and%20she%20said%20she%20had%20waited%20for%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20meeting%20was%20planned%20on%20Saturday%20after%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20surprise%20visit%20to%20the%20doctors'%20protest%20site%20at%20the%20state%20health%20secretariat.%20The%20junior%20doctors%20reached%20her%20residence%20at%206.45%20pm.%20Again%2C%20the%20doctors'%20demand%20for%20live-streaming%20and%20officials'%20refusal%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20roadblock.%20The%20medicos%20waited%20outside%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20home%20in%20the%20rain.%20They%20demanded%20that%20they%20be%20allowed%20to%20videograph%20the%20meeting.%20The%20state%20government%20refused%20this%20and%20said%20it%20would%20record%20the%20meeting%20and%20the%20recording%20would%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20doctors%20later%20because%20the%20matter%20is%20sub-judice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20came%20out%20and%20invited%20the%20doctors%20inside.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20trust%20me%2C%20I%20won't%20mislead%20you.%20Even%20if%20you%20do%20not%20attend%20the%20meeting%2C%20at%20least%20have%20a%20cup%20of%20tea.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20said%20the%20doctors%20are%20%26quot%3Binsulting%26quot%3B%20her.%20The%20doctors%20stressed%20that%20they%20wanted%20the%20recording.%20She%20then%20said%20I%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20accept%20all%20your%20demands%26quot%3B.%20Later%20that%20night%2C%20the%20doctors%20decided%20to%20join%20the%20meeting%20but%20state%20minister%20Chandrima%20Bhattacharya%20and%20chief%20secretary%20Manoj%20Pant%20told%20them%20it%20was%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726490460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fc85d5b7_mamata-banerjee_625x300_16_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctors-reply-to-mamata-banerjees-final-talks-invite-ask-key-question-6578063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Junior%20doctors%20protesting%20in%20Kolkata%20over%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government's%20%26quot%3Bfifth%20and%20final%26quot%3B%20invitation%20for%20talks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctors-reply-to-mamata-banerjees-final-talks-invite-ask-key-question-6578063%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Political%20Manipulation%2C%20Money%20Power%20Involved%3A%20Mumbai%20Actor%20On%20Illegal%20Arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMumbai%20actor%20Kadambari%20Jethwani%20has%20alleged%20that%20she%20and%20her%20family%20members%20were%20illegally%20arrested%20by%20three%20officers%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20police%20to%20help%20save%20a%20corporate%20bigwig%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20against%20whom%20she%20filed%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20case.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20she%20said%20the%20arrest%20and%20seizure%20of%20her%20cellphone%20and%20other%20electronic%20devices%20were%20illegal%2C%20and%20that%20amounted%20to%20%26quot%3Bdeprivation%20of%20democratic%20and%20human%20rights%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%2C%20she%20said%2C%20was%20carefully%20timed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20place%20while%20her%20sexual%20harassment%20case%20was%20to%20be%20heard%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20because%20of%20her%20absence%2C%20the%20case%20was%20closed.%20She%20said%20she%20was%20arrested%20on%20February%203%20--%20days%20before%20the%20court%20case%20hearing%2C%20for%20which%20there%20was%20the%20February%205-9%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20officers%20--%20P%20S%20R%20Anjaneyulu%20(DG%20Rank)%2C%20Kanthi%20Rana%20Tata%20(I