%20for%20honest%20conversation%20and%20dialogue%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Priyanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20parents%2C%20we%20must%20not%20push%20our%20hopes%20and%20dreams%20on%20our%20children.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20recognise%20that%20they%20are%20their%20own%20individual.%20Build%20a%20space%20where%20they%20feel%20comfortable%20coming%20and%20sharing%20their%20troubles%20with%20you.%20Equip%20your%20kids%20with%20the%20skills%20to%20speak%20about%20their%20feelings%20and%20learn%20to%20manage%20them%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20build%20resilience%20and%20awareness%20in%20coping%20with%20distress%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20Engage%20with%20children%20calmly%20and%20understand%20what%20they%20are%20going%20through.%20Help%20them%20develop%20problem-solving%20skills%20early%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20stresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20anyone%20struggling%2C%20the%20mental%20health%20professional%20urges%20them%20to%20seek%20help%20right%20at%20the%20beginning.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20feeling%20depressed%20or%20low%20for%20over%20a%20week%20or%2010%20days%2C%20please%20go%20ahead%20and%20speak%20to%20someone.%20If%20you%20are%20struggling%20to%20find%20motivation%20and%20resilience%20to%20power%20through%20something%20and%20it%20is%20really%20weighing%20you%20down%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F274677%2Fmumbai-man-innovates-anti-suicide-rods-kota-hostels-bags-shark-tank-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplease%20seek%20assistance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20something%20is%20weighing%20you%20down%20and%20you%20are%20feeling%20suicidal%2C%20step%20away%20from%20the%20situation.%20Go%20and%20speak%20to%20someone%20you%20trust.%20If%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20find%20anyon